№ A3154, 16-я эскадрилья КЛК 
| bgcolor=#4F7930  align="center" width="75" | [[File:Miecze.svg|55px]]
| align="center" width="150" | [[File:HalberstadtDII.jpg|150px]] <br /> '''Halberstadt D.II''' [[File:Cross-Pattee-Heraldry.svg|15px]] <br /> Jagdstaffel 11
