|-bgcolor=#FF0000 
| align="center" width="150" | [[File:Q 045379Nieuport17.jpg|150px]] <br /> [[File:RAF type A roundel.svg|15px]] '''[[Nieuport 17]]''' <br /> № A6645, 60-я эскадрилья КЛК 
