| align="center" width="150" | [[File:Royal Aircraft Factory F.E.2 ExCC.jpg|150px]] <br /> [[File:RAF type A roundel.svg|15px]] '''F.E.2b''' <br /> № 7020, 11-я эскадрилья КЛК
