| align="center" width="75" | [[File:Miecze.svg|55px]]
| align="center" width="150" | [[File:Fokdri.jpg|150px]] <br /> <span style="color:white;">'''Fokker F.I''' [[File:Cross-Pattee-Heraldry.svg|15px]] <br /> № 102/17, Jagdstaffel 11</span>
