| align="center" width="150" | [[File:AFC de Havilland DH 5 Scout plane Sept 1917.jpg|150px]] <br /> [[File:RAF type A roundel.svg|15px]] '''DH.5''' <br /> № A9299, 64-я эскадрилья КЛК
